rows.label: qst200604_0010
rows.name:
...Demon beast it may be, but in the
end a beast. It was no match for me.

rows.label: qst200604_0020
rows.name: ...We beat it.

rows.label: qst200604_0030
rows.name: ...Yeah, we beat it.

rows.label: qst200604_0040
rows.name:
I gotta say, I didn't think
we'd actually do it.

rows.label: qst200604_0050
rows.name:
Good heavens, what are
you all staring at?

rows.label: qst200604_0060
rows.name:
An enemy of this level, it is
only natural that we defeat it.

rows.label: qst200604_0070
rows.name:
On the contrary, you should be
ashamed that we struggled this much.

rows.label: qst200604_0080
rows.name: Hah...

rows.label: qst200604_0090
rows.name:
But you know, a serious
Kubira is pretty amazing.

rows.label: qst200604_0100
rows.name:
Indeed. I thought he was hiding his power,
but I never imagined it was this much.

rows.label: qst200604_0110
rows.name: I'm truly glad he's not our enemy.

rows.label: qst200604_0120
rows.name: Are you worried about your lost country?

rows.label: qst200604_0130
rows.name: ...As you can see.

rows.label: qst200604_0140
rows.name:
An enemy of this level is easily
defeated when I get serious.

rows.label: qst200604_0150
rows.name:
But... even if I defeat it, it won't
bring back my ruined kingdom...

rows.label: qst200604_0160
rows.name:
And there is no way to confirm if
that country was my kingdom...

rows.label: qst200604_0170
rows.name: Kubira...

rows.label: qst200604_0180
rows.name: What's with the gloomy face?

rows.label: qst200604_0190
rows.name:
No need to worry about that. If you
want a kingdom, just make a new one!

rows.label: qst200604_0200
rows.name: That's right.

rows.label: qst200604_0210
rows.name:
If Kubira gets serious, he can
make it happen in no time.

rows.label: qst200604_0220
rows.name: I see. Your counsel is most sound.

rows.label: qst200604_0230
rows.name: Now that my revenge is complete...

rows.label: qst200604_0240
rows.name:
It is the height of folly for I,
a king, to be bound by the past.

rows.label: qst200604_0250
rows.name: My path of conquest is still ongoing.

rows.label: qst200604_0260
rows.name:
Then, it is inevitable that I shall once
again become the king who rules this world.

rows.label: qst200604_0270
rows.name: [ML:undisp ]Haaahahahahaha!

rows.label: qst200604_0280
rows.name: ...It's good that he's motivated, but...

rows.label: qst200604_0290
rows.name:
I feel like he's looking in a
completely different direction, mo...

rows.label: qst200604_0300
rows.name:
Listen, your power is still unreliable. Therefore,
I shall support you with all my might.

rows.label: qst200604_0310
rows.name:
But all is for the sake
of my path of conquest.

rows.label: qst200604_0320
rows.name: Do not forget that.

rows.label: qst200604_0330
rows.name: [ML:undisp ]Haaahahahahaha!

rows.label: qst200604_0340
rows.name:
...I'm happy he's getting
fired up, but...

rows.label: qst200604_0350
rows.name: Something about it is irritating.

rows.label: qst200604_0360
rows.name: Don't say that...

rows.label: qst200604_0370
rows.name:
Even he is concerned for
us. We should be happy.

rows.label: qst200604_0380
rows.name: That's right.

rows.label: qst200604_0390
rows.name:
Taking care of people like this is
a measure of a Driver's capacity.

rows.label: qst200604_0400
rows.name: You think so...?

rows.label: qst200604_0410
rows.name: [ML:undisp ]Haaahahahahaha!
